Top-seeded Indiana, led by [Heisman Trophy winner Fernando Mendoza](https://www.foxnews.com/sports/indiana-crushes-oregon-advance-first-championship-game-program-history-stunning-sports-world), will take on Miami at Hard Rock Stadium in Miami Gardens, Florida, Monday at 7:45 p.m. ET.

